{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":809,"text":"I'm going to talk to you today"},{"time":2294,"text":"about the design of medical technology\nfor low-resource settings."},{"time":5801,"text":"I study health systems in these countries."},{"time":8178,"text":"And one of the major gaps in care,"},{"time":10117,"text":"almost across the board,"},{"time":11800,"text":"is access to safe surgery."},{"time":13991,"text":"Now one of the major\nbottlenecks that we've found"},{"time":16674,"text":"that's sort of preventing\nboth the access in the first place,"},{"time":19933,"text":"and the safety of those surgeries\nthat do happen, is anesthesia."},{"time":23846,"text":"And actually, it's the model\nthat we expect to work"},{"time":26262,"text":"for delivering anesthesia\nin these environments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29620,"text":"Here, we have a scene that you would find\nin any operating room across the US,"},{"time":33497,"text":"or any other developed country."},{"time":34998,"text":"In the background there"},{"time":36209,"text":"is a very sophisticated\nanesthesia machine."},{"time":38804,"text":"And this machine is able\nto enable surgery and save lives"},{"time":42677,"text":"because it was designed\nwith this environment in mind."},{"time":46329,"text":"In order to operate,\nthis machine needs a number of things"},{"time":49285,"text":"that this hospital has to offer."},{"time":51209,"text":"It needs an extremely\nwell-trained anesthesiologist"},{"time":54601,"text":"with years of training\nwith complex machines"},{"time":57076,"text":"to help her monitor the flows of the gas"},{"time":59521,"text":"and keep her patients\nsafe and anesthetized"},{"time":62108,"text":"throughout the surgery."},{"time":63583,"text":"It's a delicate machine\nrunning on computer algorithms,"},{"time":66374,"text":"and it needs special care, TLC,\nto keep it up and running,"},{"time":69616,"text":"and it's going to break pretty easily."},{"time":71498,"text":"And when it does, it needs\na team of biomedical engineers"},{"time":74434,"text":"who understand its complexities,\ncan fix it, can source the parts"},{"time":77767,"text":"and keep it saving lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80688,"text":"It's a pretty expensive machine."},{"time":82246,"text":"It needs a hospital\nwhose budget can allow it"},{"time":84911,"text":"to support one machine\ncosting upwards of 50 or $100,000."},{"time":90296,"text":"And perhaps most obviously,"},{"time":92219,"text":"but also most importantly --"},{"time":93757,"text":"and the path to concepts\nthat we've heard about"},{"time":96617,"text":"kind of illustrates this --"},{"time":97927,"text":"it needs infrastructure that can supply\nan uninterrupted source of electricity,"},{"time":103097,"text":"of compressed oxygen,\nand other medical supplies"},{"time":106133,"text":"that are so critical\nto the functioning of this machine."},{"time":110435,"text":"In other words, this machine\nrequires a lot of stuff"},{"time":113758,"text":"that this hospital cannot offer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116332,"text":"This is the electrical supply\nfor a hospital in rural Malawi."},{"time":120153,"text":"In this hospital,"},{"time":121338,"text":"there is one person qualified\nto deliver anesthesia,"},{"time":124033,"text":"and she's qualified"},{"time":125209,"text":"because she has 12, maybe 18 months\nof training in anesthesia."},{"time":129809,"text":"In the hospital and in the entire region"},{"time":132080,"text":"there's not a single biomedical engineer."},{"time":134111,"text":"So when this machine breaks,"},{"time":135704,"text":"the machines that they have\nto work with break,"},{"time":137937,"text":"they've got to try and figure it out,"},{"time":139730,"text":"but most of the time,\nthat's the end of the road."},{"time":142046,"text":"Those machines go the proverbial junkyard."},{"time":144287,"text":"And the price tag\nof the machine that I mentioned"},{"time":146640,"text":"could represent maybe a quarter or a third"},{"time":148725,"text":"of the annual operating budget\nfor this hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152580,"text":"And finally, I think you can see\nthat infrastructure is not very strong."},{"time":155988,"text":"This hospital is connected\nto a very weak power grid,"},{"time":158686,"text":"one that goes down frequently."},{"time":160492,"text":"So it runs frequently,\nthe entire hospital,"},{"time":163062,"text":"just on a generator."},{"time":164509,"text":"And you can imagine,\nthe generator breaks down"},{"time":166689,"text":"or runs out of fuel."},{"time":168361,"text":"And the World Bank sees this"},{"time":170412,"text":"and estimates that a hospital\nin this setting in a low-income country"},{"time":173967,"text":"can expect up to\n18 power outages per month."},{"time":178658,"text":"Similarly, compressed oxygen\nand other medical supplies"},{"time":181875,"text":"are really a luxury,"},{"time":183081,"text":"and can often be out of stock\nfor months or even a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186387,"text":"So it seems crazy, but the model\nthat we have right now"},{"time":189575,"text":"is taking those machines\nthat were designed"},{"time":191804,"text":"for that first environment\nthat I showed you"},{"time":194111,"text":"and donating or selling them\nto hospitals in this environment."},{"time":198861,"text":"It's not just inappropriate,"},{"time":200461,"text":"it becomes really unsafe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203516,"text":"One of our partners at Johns Hopkins"},{"time":205462,"text":"was observing surgeries in Sierra Leone\nabout a year ago."},{"time":210225,"text":"And the first surgery of the day\nhappened to be an obstetrical case."},{"time":213582,"text":"A woman came in,\nshe needed an emergency C-section"},{"time":216589,"text":"to save her life and the life of her baby."},{"time":219805,"text":"And everything began pretty auspiciously."},{"time":221783,"text":"The surgeon was on call and scrubbed in."},{"time":224060,"text":"The nurse was there."},{"time":225372,"text":"She was able to anesthetize her quickly,\nand it was important"},{"time":228257,"text":"because of the emergency\nnature of the situation."},{"time":230617,"text":"And everything began well"},{"time":232358,"text":"until the power went out."},{"time":235773,"text":"And now in the middle of this surgery,"},{"time":237621,"text":"the surgeon is racing\nagainst the clock to finish his case,"},{"time":240714,"text":"which he can do -- he's got a headlamp."},{"time":243090,"text":"But the nurse is literally running\naround a darkened operating theater"},{"time":247175,"text":"trying to find anything\nshe can use to anesthetize her patient,"},{"time":250154,"text":"to keep her patient asleep."},{"time":251867,"text":"Because her machine doesn't work\nwhen there's no power."},{"time":255437,"text":"This routine surgery that many of you\nhave probably experienced,"},{"time":258515,"text":"and others are probably the product of,\nhas now become a tragedy."},{"time":263655,"text":"And what's so frustrating\nis this is not a singular event;"},{"time":266415,"text":"this happens across the developing world."},{"time":268938,"text":"35 million surgeries\nare attempted every year"},{"time":271915,"text":"without safe anesthesia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274210,"text":"My colleague, Dr. Paul Fenton,\nwas living this reality."},{"time":277146,"text":"He was the chief of anesthesiology"},{"time":279000,"text":"in a hospital in Malawi,\na teaching hospital."},{"time":282028,"text":"He went to work every day"},{"time":283546,"text":"in an operating theater like this one,"},{"time":285538,"text":"trying to deliver anesthesia\nand teach others how to do so"},{"time":288701,"text":"using that same equipment"},{"time":290000,"text":"that became so unreliable,\nand frankly unsafe, in his hospital."},{"time":295039,"text":"And after umpteen surgeries"},{"time":296843,"text":"and, you can imagine,\nreally unspeakable tragedy,"},{"time":299435,"text":"he just said, \"That's it.\nI'm done. That's enough."},{"time":301801,"text":"There has to be something better.\""},{"time":304229,"text":"He took a walk down the hall"},{"time":305800,"text":"to where they threw all those machines\nthat had just crapped out on them,"},{"time":309255,"text":"I think that's the scientific term,"},{"time":310956,"text":"and he started tinkering."},{"time":312322,"text":"He took one part from here\nand another from there,"},{"time":314699,"text":"and he tried to come up\nwith a machine that would work"},{"time":317305,"text":"in the reality that he was facing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318957,"text":"And what he came up with:"},{"time":320195,"text":"was this guy."},{"time":321542,"text":"The prototype for the Universal\nAnesthesia Machine --"},{"time":325103,"text":"a machine that would work\nand anesthetize his patients"},{"time":328424,"text":"no matter the circumstances\nthat his hospital had to offer."},{"time":332519,"text":"Here it is, back at home"},{"time":334024,"text":"at that same hospital, developed\na little further, 12 years later,"},{"time":337477,"text":"working on patients\nfrom pediatrics to geriatrics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341137,"text":"Let me show you a little bit\nabout how this machine works."},{"time":343931,"text":"Voila!"},{"time":346452,"text":"Here she is."},{"time":347683,"text":"When you have electricity,"},{"time":348951,"text":"everything in this machine\nbegins in the base."},{"time":351993,"text":"There's a built-in\noxygen concentrator down there."},{"time":354614,"text":"Now you've heard me mention\noxygen a few times at this point."},{"time":357767,"text":"Essentially, to deliver anesthesia,\nyou want as pure oxygen as possible,"},{"time":361579,"text":"because eventually you're going\nto dilute it, essentially, with the gas."},{"time":365026,"text":"And the mixture that the patient inhales"},{"time":367486,"text":"needs to be at least\na certain percentage oxygen"},{"time":369821,"text":"or else it can become dangerous."},{"time":371531,"text":"But so in here when there's electricity,"},{"time":373473,"text":"the oxygen concentrator takes in room air."},{"time":376372,"text":"Now we know room air is gloriously free,"},{"time":379675,"text":"it is abundant,"},{"time":381000,"text":"and it's already 21 percent oxygen."},{"time":383436,"text":"So all this concentrator does\nis take that room air in, filter it"},{"time":387137,"text":"and send 95 percent pure oxygen\nup and across here,"},{"time":390981,"text":"where it mixes with the anesthetic agent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393743,"text":"Now before that mixture\nhits the patient's lungs,"},{"time":397391,"text":"it's going to pass by here --\nyou can't see it,"},{"time":399629,"text":"but there's an oxygen sensor here --"},{"time":401435,"text":"that's going to read out on this screen\nthe percentage of oxygen being delivered."},{"time":406284,"text":"Now if you don't have power,"},{"time":408282,"text":"or, God forbid, the power cuts out\nin the middle of a surgery,"},{"time":411912,"text":"this machine transitions automatically,"},{"time":414280,"text":"without even having to touch it,"},{"time":416053,"text":"to drawing in room air from this inlet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418805,"text":"Everything else is the same."},{"time":420165,"text":"The only difference is that now"},{"time":421785,"text":"you're only working\nwith 21 percent oxygen."},{"time":425406,"text":"Now that used to be\na dangerous guessing game,"},{"time":428251,"text":"because you only knew\nif you gave too little oxygen"},{"time":430661,"text":"once something bad happened."},{"time":432061,"text":"But we've put a long-life\nbattery backup on here."},{"time":434798,"text":"This is the only part\nthat's battery backed up."},{"time":437016,"text":"But this gives control to the provider,\nwhether there's power or not,"},{"time":440445,"text":"because they can adjust the flows"},{"time":442062,"text":"based on the percentage of oxygen\nthey see that they're giving the patient."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446054,"text":"In both cases,\nwhether you have power or not,"},{"time":449423,"text":"sometimes the patient\nneeds help breathing."},{"time":451487,"text":"It's just a reality of anesthesia,\nthe lungs can be paralyzed."},{"time":454712,"text":"And so we've just added\nthis manual bellows."},{"time":456820,"text":"We've seen surgeries\nfor three or four hours"},{"time":459835,"text":"to ventilate the patient on this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462424,"text":"So it's a straightforward machine."},{"time":465436,"text":"I shudder to say simple;\nit's straightforward."},{"time":468936,"text":"And it's by design."},{"time":470861,"text":"You do not need to be a highly trained,\nspecialized anesthesiologist"},{"time":476085,"text":"to use this machine,"},{"time":477280,"text":"which is good because,\nin these rural district hospitals,"},{"time":480056,"text":"you're not going to get\nthat level of training."},{"time":482675,"text":"It's also designed for the environment\nthat it will be used in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485827,"text":"This is an incredibly rugged machine."},{"time":487628,"text":"It has to stand up to the heat\nand the wear and tear"},{"time":491107,"text":"that happens in hospitals\nin these rural districts."},{"time":494249,"text":"And so it's not going\nto break very easily,"},{"time":496668,"text":"but if it does, virtually\nevery piece in this machine"},{"time":499966,"text":"can be swapped out and replaced"},{"time":502000,"text":"with a hex wrench and a screwdriver."},{"time":505750,"text":"And finally, it's affordable."},{"time":508034,"text":"This machine comes in\nat an eighth of the cost"},{"time":511711,"text":"of the conventional machine\nthat I showed you earlier."},{"time":514813,"text":"So in other words, what we have here\nis a machine that can enable surgery"},{"time":519325,"text":"and save lives,"},{"time":520521,"text":"because it was designed\nfor its environment,"},{"time":523535,"text":"just like the first machine I showed you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525977,"text":"But we're not content to stop there."},{"time":528005,"text":"Is it working?"},{"time":529204,"text":"Is this the design\nthat's going to work in place?"},{"time":531810,"text":"Well, we've seen good results so far."},{"time":533601,"text":"This is in 13 hospitals in four countries,"},{"time":537010,"text":"and since 2010, we've done\nwell over 2,000 surgeries"},{"time":540967,"text":"with no clinically adverse events."},{"time":543540,"text":"So we're thrilled."},{"time":544731,"text":"This really seems like\na cost-effective, scalable solution"},{"time":549177,"text":"to a problem that's really pervasive."},{"time":551698,"text":"But we still want to be sure"},{"time":553322,"text":"that this is the most effective\nand safe device"},{"time":555763,"text":"that we can be putting into hospitals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557844,"text":"So to do that, we've launched\na number of partnerships"},{"time":560392,"text":"with NGOs and universities,"},{"time":561902,"text":"to gather data on the user interface,"},{"time":564575,"text":"on the types of surgeries\nit's appropriate for,"},{"time":566791,"text":"and ways we can enhance the device itself."},{"time":569202,"text":"One of those partnerships\nis with Johns Hopkins"},{"time":571880,"text":"just here in Baltimore."},{"time":573277,"text":"They have a really cool anesthesia\nsimulation lab out in Baltimore."},{"time":577579,"text":"So we're taking this machine"},{"time":579484,"text":"and recreating some\nof the operating theater crises"},{"time":583082,"text":"that this machine might face"},{"time":584613,"text":"in one of the hospitals\nthat it's intended for,"},{"time":587000,"text":"and in a contained, safe environment,"},{"time":589148,"text":"evaluating its effectiveness."},{"time":591347,"text":"We're then able to compare\nthe results from that study"},{"time":595003,"text":"with real-world experience,"},{"time":596447,"text":"because we're putting\ntwo of these in hospitals"},{"time":598668,"text":"that Johns Hopkins\nworks with in Sierra Leone,"},{"time":600843,"text":"including the hospital\nwhere that emergency C-section happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605385,"text":"So I've talked a lot about anesthesia,\nand I tend to do that."},{"time":608537,"text":"I think it is incredibly fascinating\nand an important component of health."},{"time":612653,"text":"And it really seems peripheral,\nwe never think about it,"},{"time":615308,"text":"until we don't have access to it,"},{"time":617536,"text":"and then it becomes a gatekeeper."},{"time":619522,"text":"Who gets surgery and who doesn't?"},{"time":621824,"text":"Who gets safe surgery and who doesn't?"},{"time":625216,"text":"But you know,\nit's just one of so many ways"},{"time":627703,"text":"that design, appropriate design,"},{"time":630834,"text":"can have an impact on health outcomes."},{"time":633318,"text":"If more people\nin the health-delivery space"},{"time":635461,"text":"really working on some of these\nchallenges in low-income countries"},{"time":639054,"text":"could start their design process,\ntheir solution search,"},{"time":642731,"text":"from outside of that proverbial box"},{"time":644693,"text":"and inside of the hospital --"},{"time":646655,"text":"In other words, if we could design"},{"time":648510,"text":"for the environment that exists\nin so many parts of the world,"},{"time":651725,"text":"rather than the one\nthat we wished existed --"},{"time":654158,"text":"we might just save a lot of lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656787,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658279,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}